<subSubSection id="A2D3C1A9FF9D3846FF25D465FB35AC13" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="EA769222FF9D3846FF25D465FB35AC13" blockId="7.[151,1437,1100,1809]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">
<emphasis id="D8BD4E30FF9D3846FF25D465FEACAD83" bold="true" box="[199,315,1640,1665]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species differs significantly from the other species on Hainan island, 
<taxonomicName id="2DC9E9A1FF9D3846FB4BD464FADFAD82" box="[1193,1352,1641,1664]" class="Insecta" family="Blephariceridae" genus="Blepharicera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="macropyga">
<emphasis id="D8BD4E30FF9D3846FB4BD464FADFAD82" box="[1193,1352,1641,1664]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">B. macropyga</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in the hypandrium not forming a large keel and in the coloration of wings (light brown with obviously white net-like lines). The shape of the male genitalia of this species differs from that of other species of Chinese 
<taxonomicName id="2DC9E9A1FF9D3846FB09D4BCFAE8ADCB" box="[1259,1407,1713,1737]" class="Insecta" family="Blephariceridae" genus="Blepharicera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D8BD4E30FF9D3846FB09D4BCFAE8ADCB" box="[1259,1407,1713,1737]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Blepharicera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the shape of the epandrium (posterior margin round) and cercus (narrow bridge separating two lobes). In other known species, both cercal lobes are near to each other (
<bibRefCitation id="8E58EFD3FF9D3846FCEFD4F5FC2EAC13" author="Kitakami" box="[781,953,1784,1809]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" refString="Kitakami, S. (1937) Supplementary notes on the Blephariceridae of Japan. Memoirs of the College of Sciences, Kyoto Imperial University, 12, 115 - 136." type="journal article" year="1937">Kitakami 1937</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="8E58EFD3FF9D3846FC26D4F5FC68AC13" author="Kitakami" box="[964,1023,1784,1809]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" refString="Kitakami, S. (1950) The revision of the Blephariceridae of Japan and adjacent territories. The Journal of Kumamoto Women's University, 2, 15 - 90." type="journal article" year="1950">1950</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="8E58EFD3FF9D3846FBE9D4F5FB01AC13" author="Zwick" box="[1035,1174,1784,1809]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" refString="Zwick, P. (1990) Systematic notes on Holarctic Blephariceridae (Diptera). Bonner Zoologische Beitraege, 41, 231 - 257." type="journal article" year="1990">
Zwick 
<number id="5C018005FF9D3846FBB8D4F4FB01AC13" box="[1114,1174,1785,1809]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" value="1990.0">1990</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
